definition.value: Category=gene. Despite the gene and protein name, this is not a 1:1 ortholog of the human IFIT1 gene product. It appears that the mouse/human speciation was followed by duplication of the progenitor gene in each species. This duplication appears to have preceded the human/chimp and mouse/rat speciation.
